Package edu.csus.ecs.pc2.api.exceptions

PC2 API exceptions.

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    LoadContestDataException
    Exception loading contest data (contest.yaml).
    LoginFailureException
    This class defines the Exception which is thrown when a failure occurs during a client's attempt to connect to a PC2 server through the PC2 API.
    NotLoggedInException
    Signals that an attempt has been made to call a method when a client is not logged in.

Package edu.csus.ecs.pc2.api.exceptions Description

PC2 API exceptions.

This documentation describes the current draft of the PC2 API, which is subject to change.
